for the first to connect with github with your local machine first follow the code 
open the new folder or existance folder open the bash here,then enter this code
"git clone <--link-->", pass enter, it will work only for the first time 
Then github repository file will save in local system 
 "git pull" command is use to get the file from github repository

"ls" command to use list we have in github repository
"cat <---file name--->"it is use to display the file details
if you want to edit the file and again update the file commit changes it save the edit file.






